[19.710719, "o", "23\\t * @param {boolean} opt.dontCrossCorners Disallow diagonal movement touching\\n24\\t *     block corners. Deprecated, use diagonalMovement instead.\\n25\\t * @param {DiagonalMovement} opt.diagonalMovement Allowed diagonal movement.\\n26\\t * @param {function} opt.heuristic Heuristic function to estimate the distance\\n27\\t *     (defaults to manhattan).\\n28\\t * @param {number} opt.weight Weight to apply to the heuristic to allow for\\n29\\t *     suboptimal paths, in order to speed up the search.\\n30\\t * @param {boolean} opt.trackRecursion Whether to track recursion for\\n31\\t *     statistical purposes.\\n32\\t * @param {number} opt.timeLimit Maximum execution time. Use <= 0 for infinite.\\n33\\t */\\n34\\tfunction IDAStarFinder(opt) {\\n35\\t    opt = opt || {};\\n36\\t    this.allowDiagonal = opt.allowDiagonal;\\n37\\t    this.dontCrossCorners = opt.dontCrossCorners;\\n38\\t    this.diagonalMovement = opt.diagonalMovement;\\n39\\t    this.heuristic = opt.heuristic || Heuristic.manhattan;\\n40\\t    this.weight = opt.weight || 1;\\"]
